

--to run springboot in dubug mode from cmd
>mvn spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.jvmArguments="-agentlib:jdwp=transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=5005"

to skip all tests in maveen
    pom property
         <skipTests>true</skipTests>
    you can also toggle skip mode buttion
    you can append to maveen run command like below
        mvn clean install site -DskipTests
to skip unit tests in maveen
     <skipUTs>true</skipUTs>
    mvn clean install site -DskipUTs